highlights.text: “天空没有極限 (粤)” by G.E.M. is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Hong Kong, up 52 spots at #44.
“零距离的思念” by TINY 7 has been on Viral Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 131 days straight.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Hong Kong. “Golden” is the highest at #2.
“Dandelion” by go!go!vanillas is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Hong Kong at #70.
